        "text": "### Stability Constants (log β, ML formation, aqueous, 25 °C)\n\n| Rank | Ligand | Abbreviation | log β (ML) | I (M) | SRD-46 ID |\n|------|--------|-------------|-----------|-------|-----------|\n| 1 | Diethylenetrinitrilopentaacetic acid | **DTPA** | **19.48** | 0.1 | ligand_6356 |\n| 2 | Ethylenedinitrilo-N,N′-di(3-propanoic) type | **EDPA-type** | **17.20** | 0.1 | ligand_6309 |\n| 3 | Ethylenedinitrilotetraacetic acid | **EDTA** | **15.46** | 0.1 | ligand_6277 |\n| 4 | Nitrilotriacetic acid | **NTA** | **10.36** | 0.1 | ligand_6165 |\n\nAdditional La³⁺ carboxylate systems present in SRD-46 include *trans*-CDTA (ligand_6301), EDDA (ligand_6267), EGTA (ligand_6335), iminodiacetic acid/IDA (ligand_6127), diglycolic acid (ligand_8974), and dipicolinic acid (ligand_6774), all at 25 °C.",
